The game :

-You must passed the 3 missionnaries on the right bank of the river.
-The boat can transport 2 persons or at least 1
 (Click anyware, if you don't want the second person)
-If on one bank of the river, there is more cannibals than missionnaries, you loose.


Quit the game with 'ESC'

There is a stero effect when the boat move.
Use SPACE key to switch the canals (left & right) is needed.

This game is freeware.

